 competency mastery,
 certification currency,
 and training completion shall be verified at least annually through a documented competency assessment.
 For personnel subject to formal performance reviews,
 the competency assessment may be conducted as part of the performance review process.
 The IT Director shall confirm that each individual maintains the current certifications and training completions required by the assigned tier in 
\series bold
Appendix 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
