reference "app:6.03"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
 For the IT Director,
 the annual verification of certification currency,
 training completion,
 and assigned-tier competency requirements shall be performed or approved by the County Manager.
 Lapses shall trigger the access-eligibility consequences defined in Section 6.1 and any account actions required under 
\series bold
Policy 
