\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.5 Role Vacancy and Continuity
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
To ensure continuity of critical information operations,
 the following requirements govern role vacancy management.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Succession Designation
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall designate at least one (1) individual capable of providing interim coverage for each Tier L3 and above role.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Documentation
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall document succession designations in the Department's system of record.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Annual Review
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall review succession designations at least annually.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Immediate Coverage
\series default
:
 Upon an unplanned vacancy in any Tier L3+ role,
 the IT Director shall activate interim delegation under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:1.08"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 within one (1) business day.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
IT Director Vacancy — Interim Authority
\series default
:
 In the event of an IT Director vacancy,
 the Assistant IT Director shall assume interim operational authority under the standing delegation framework established in 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:1.08"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Notification
\series default
:
 The Assistant IT Director shall formally notify the County Manager of the vacancy within one (1) business day.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Backfill
\series default
:
 The County Manager shall initiate permanent backfill or role restructuring within thirty (30) calendar days of notification.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Extended Vacancy
\series default
:
 If a Tier L3+ vacancy (other than IT Director) exceeds sixty (60) calendar days without permanent backfill or a documented restructuring decision,
 the IT Director shall prepare a risk assessment identifying competency gaps,
 coverage limitations,
 and compensating controls.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Submission
\series default
:
 The IT Director shall submit the risk assessment to the County Manager.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_layout

